snippet.title: Tony Hawk's Underground 2 Remix Trailer
snippet.description:
This was from Demo Disc 20 Special Edition of the PS2 Official Magazine.

This trailer is Tony Hawk's Underground 2 Remix

Notes from Uploader:
This is the only PSP trailer from the disc that isn't just a small video on a picture of a PSP.
I am honestly impressed for someone in 2005 to be casually making big combos like this guy in the trailer did.
